# Database Rules

- Understand existing schema before changing queries.
- Preserve data ownership and tenant isolation.
- Avoid destructive queries without explicit confirmation.
- Avoid N+1 queries.
- Keep indexes in mind for frequent filters.
- Do not add migrations if the project explicitly does not use migrations.
